#Plot p value vs fold change, all peaks
EnhancedVolcano(H3K36me3_NPC_anno, lab = NA,
                x = 'Fold',
                y = 'p.value',
                xlim = c(-25, 25), title = "H3K36me3 peaks, max-gap 20",
                drawConnectors = TRUE, max.overlaps = Inf, widthConnectors = 0.25, arrowheads = TRUE,
                col=c("Black", "Dark grey", "Dark grey", "#A92003"), colAlpha = 1)

#Plot p value vs fold change, 37 (35) genes labeled

## Extact 37 genes from our finding and label
genes <- read.csv("~/Doktorssnam/data/RNASeq in vivo/comparison_RNASeq_CUTRUN/human_ortholog_RNASEQ_3datasets_up_SMYD5_bound_SMYD5_KO_UP_DEG_shared_genes.csv", sep="")

EnhancedVolcano(H3K36me3_NPC_anno, lab = H3K36me3_NPC_anno$SYMBOL, 
                selectLab = c(genes$human_37genes_upregulated_SMYD5_downregulated), labSize = 2.0,
                x = 'Fold',
                y = 'p.value',
                xlim = c(-25, 25), title = "H3K36me3 peaks, max-gap 20",
                drawConnectors = TRUE, max.overlaps = Inf, widthConnectors = 0.25, arrowheads = TRUE,
